      "text": "so where do you get the money from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 229461.0,
      "end_time": 231797.0,
      "text": "Well, the United States is a low-low tax country"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 231830.0,
      "end_time": 233466.0,
      "text": "by OECD standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 233499.0,
      "end_time": 235501.0,
      "text": "-I heard it&#39;s the highest taxes in the world. -It is not."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 235534.0,
      "end_time": 237690.0,
      "text": "It is not even close to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 237102.0,
      "end_time": 239305.0,
      "text": "And the government does less redistribution"
