    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 241507.0,
      "end_time": 243242.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s part of the reason that we have the kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 243275.0,
      "end_time": 245411.0,
      "text": "of wage stagnation and inequality that we&#39;ve had."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 245444.0,
