      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 265640.0,
      "end_time": 266899.0,
      "text": "for really big ideas--"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 266932.0,
      "end_time": 269702.0,
      "text": "it might not be popular, it might not be easy to pass--"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 269735.0,
      "end_time": 272400.0,
      "text": "but the money it out there, that&#39;s not the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 272370.0,
      "end_time": 274739.0,
      "text": "If you look at people who are already paying tax,"
