    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 290890.0,
      "end_time": 291557.0,
      "text": "How would you respond to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 291590.0,
      "end_time": 293626.0,
      "text": "So it probably wouldn&#39;t be everybody"
