    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 309942.0,
      "end_time": 312111.0,
      "text": "The United States has a rate of child poverty"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 312144.0,
      "end_time": 314280.0,
      "text": "that is two, three, even four times as high"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 314313.0,
      "end_time": 316949.0,
      "text": "as in similar countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 316982.0,
      "end_time": 319251.0,
      "text": "And so the idea here is that, you know, right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 319284.0,
      "end_time": 321454.0,
      "text": "we have a safety net with gaping holes in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 321487.0,
      "end_time": 324890.0,
      "text": "We allow and we choose for people to be in poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 324923.0,
      "end_time": 326726.0,
      "text": "Even now, with the good economy that we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 326759.0,
      "end_time": 328494.0,
      "text": "one in seven Americans is in poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 328527.0,
      "end_time": 330763.0,
      "text": "more than 20% of children."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 330796.0,
      "end_time": 332465.0,
      "text": "And so the safety net that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 332498.0,
      "end_time": 334166.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t working in a lot of cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 334199.0,
      "end_time": 336435.0,
      "text": "And so I think that you&#39;ve seen a lot of, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 336468.0,
      "end_time": 338404.0,
      "text": "political strife and concerns about inequality"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 338437.0,
      "end_time": 340773.0,
      "text": "in this country, and this, like, feeling that there&#39;s a need"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 340806.0,
      "end_time": 343508.0,
      "text": "for bigger solutions if the problem is going to be so big."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 343542.0,
      "end_time": 346811.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a powerful issue that, uh, I mean, everyone is debating."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 346845.0,
      "end_time": 349515.0,
      "text": "You have many tech leaders joining in and saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 349548.0,
      "end_time": 350916.0,
      "text": "\"I think we need to look at this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 350949.0,
      "end_time": 353252.0,
      "text": "President Obama, in South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 353285.0,
      "end_time": 354920.0,
      "text": "in his speech actually just said the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 354953.0,
      "end_time": 356255.0,
      "text": "He said maybe we should be looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 356288.0,
      "end_time": 358290.0,
      "text": "at universal basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 358323.0,
      "end_time": 361827.0,
      "text": "There is, I guess, one question that would always loom over it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 361860.0,
      "end_time": 363696.0,
      "text": "and that is, historically, in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 363729.0,
      "end_time": 365865.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d be naive to propose"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 365898.0,
      "end_time": 368267.0,
      "text": "any idea involving giving people money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 368300.0,
      "end_time": 371170.0,
      "text": "if we don&#39;t acknowledge that race will always come into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 371203.0,
      "end_time": 374106.0,
      "text": "-There&#39;ll be a factor, and that is race. -Yes. Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 374139.0,
      "end_time": 375508.0,
      "text": "Do you think it is a program"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 375541.0,
      "end_time": 377376.0,
      "text": "that could be passed in America?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 377409.0,
      "end_time": 380880.0,
      "text": "Thinking of how ,like, welfare has been attacked, etc., etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 380913.0,
      "end_time": 383480.0,
      "text": "Yeah, it&#39;s a real challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 383810.0,
      "end_time": 385284.0,
      "text": "So the reason that we don&#39;t have the kind of safety net"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 385317.0,
      "end_time": 387186.0,
      "text": "that you see in sort of similar countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 387219.0,
      "end_time": 389355.0,
      "text": "whether Canada or Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 389388.0,
      "end_time": 391991.0,
      "text": "is largely because of race and racism, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 392240.0,
      "end_time": 395600.0,
      "text": "We, as a country, have just really hated the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 395930.0,
      "end_time": 397563.0,
      "text": "of giving money to people, and then, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 397596.0,
      "end_time": 399565.0,
      "text": "we judge them for how they use it, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 399598.0,
      "end_time": 402100.0,
      "text": "You see this embedded in the programs that we already have."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 402340.0,
      "end_time": 404670.0,
      "text": "You know, if you have food stamps or SNAP benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 404703.0,
      "end_time": 407405.0,
      "text": "we say you can buy this kind of food but not that kind of food."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 407439.0,
      "end_time": 409575.0,
      "text": "And we have a lot of requirements for programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 409608.0,
      "end_time": 412778.0,
      "text": "that very low-income people use."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 412811.0,
      "end_time": 414780.0,
      "text": "And so this would be a counterbalance to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 414813.0,
      "end_time": 417820.0,
      "text": "but I do think it&#39;s right that, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 417115.0,
      "end_time": 419285.0,
      "text": "you would have a large group of people in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 419318.0,
      "end_time": 422854.0,
      "text": "and we have a culture that really valorizes work"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 422888.0,
      "end_time": 424657.0,
      "text": "that would object to this and say, you know, like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 424690.0,
      "end_time": 426392.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m just not okay with that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 426425.0,
      "end_time": 427893.0,
      "text": "I do think that it&#39;s a very big challenge to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 427926.0,
      "end_time": 429829.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not a reason not to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 429862.0,
      "end_time": 432565.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a challenge, it&#39;s exciting, it&#39;s fascinating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 432598.0,
      "end_time": 434233.0,
      "text": "and, uh, it&#39;s one of the reasons I enjoyed the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 434266.0,
      "end_time": 435701.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much for being on the show."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 435734.0,
      "end_time": 437736.0,
      "text": "-Thank you. -I really appreciate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 437769.0,
      "end_time": 439738.0,
      "text": "Give People Money  is available now."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 439771.0,
      "end_time": 441371.0,
      "text": "Annie Lowrey, everybody."
    }
  ]
}